overview: A group of three talented rock stars, the Kittens, have formed around their singer, Kitana. She has everything going for her: she is beautiful, she sings well and pleases fans and producers a lot… Simply, everything is not always so easy to break into the industry, because girls are sometimes faced with intrigues that they must surpass to hope to be propelled on the front of the stage! But between stories of sex, manipulation and jealousy, they always achieve their ends ..
title: Rock'n'Sex
